1. Introduction
These Terms of Service (“Terms”) govern your use of the Discord bots and related services (“Services”) provided by Madison Beal (operating as madsbx). By commissioning, subscribing to, or otherwise using the Services, you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, you must not use the Services.

2. Scope of Services
I create and host custom Discord bots designed for specific servers and communities.
Services include but are not limited to: server utilities (moderation tools, auto-roles, welcome messages), interactive features (games, levelling systems, gacha tracking), and custom feature development as agreed.
Bots are hosted via GitHub, deployed via Railway, and supported with PostgreSQL databases.

3. Payments & Fees
Subscription Fees: Monthly subscription fees are based on server member count. Fees cover hosting, network/CPU usage, and database maintenance.
Payment Methods: All payments must be processed through PayPal Goods & Services. Tips are optional via Ko-Fi.
Taxes: All prices are subject to 15% Harmonized Sales Tax (HST) under New Brunswick law due to pricing structures. 
Fee Adjustments: If your server size increases or hosting usage exceeds the original agreement, I reserve the right to adjust fees with 30 days’ written notice.
Non-Payment: Failure to pay may result in suspension or termination of bot services.

