You agree to comply with Discord’s Terms of Service and Community Guidelines.
You are responsible for moderating the conduct of your server members when interacting with the bot.
You may not sell or redistribute the bot or its code without my prior written consent.

5. Termination of Services
Immediate Termination: I reserve the right to terminate Services immediately without refund if bots are used for prohibited or illegal activity.
Voluntary Termination: Either party may cancel the Service at any time. If I cancel without cause, I will provide at least 60 days’ notice. 
Cancellation Notice Period: You must give at least 7 days notice (including weekends) in advance of your expected billing date for termination of services.
Refunds: Refunds will not be issued for partial months or terminated contracts unless required by law.

